---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog | Marex Ventures
description: Thoughts on custom software, AI automation, and scaling modern businesses.
---

<section class="container section" style="padding-top: 150px; padding-bottom: 4rem;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
    <h1 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Insights & <span class="text-gradient">Case Studies</span></h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--text-muted);">
      Strategies for scaling operations, automating workflows, and building exact systems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-3" style="gap: 2rem;">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
    <div class="floating-card" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
      {% if post.data.image %}
      <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
      {% endif %}
      <div style="padding: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color: var(--accent-navy); text-decoration: none;">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color: var(--accent-red); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.95rem;">Read Article &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p style="grid-column: span 3; text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted);">More insights coming soon.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
